{"tid":1890362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：300廠家查詢資助生產口罩計劃　惟符合要求不多","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T08:12:26.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d41c0a3cb56f08b9bcf24b9900bb22669e33f67","tid":1890362,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華在立法會財委會表示，有300多個廠家查詢當局資助本地生產口罩的計劃，但當中同時有機器、材料、廠房，生產質量亦達標的廠家並不多，生產力促進局會審核。他又表示，如果受資助的20條生產線投入運作，政府一個月將可以認購最多4000萬個口罩，預料一半可供內部、醫管局和外判工等使用，如果有剩餘口罩，政府會提供給有需要界別，以及作儲備之用。<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局長劉怡翔表示，政府採購口罩並非只是在辦公室「等單到」，當局正於全球六大洲300多個國家中的600多間廠家採購，上月至今已經有550萬個口罩抵港，但很多時候不同批次來港都有延誤，當中有部份口罩品質不符合要求而不收貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265743&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1265743%26csid%3D261_341&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=c695e754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265743&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"c1c9e84e8e00c291ae8b7ba47230c22445c57b1c","tid":1890362,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"成個月先搵到550萬個口罩, 夠香港人用幾多日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a97f66de3e9ab617f58c24ba5ab3df3d067a3e2","tid":1890362,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"期貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣好似炒燶石油咁,打後幾年要挨貴貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d387c40300090e84bc4f74ed45618a4164baf1e4","tid":1890362,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:11:05.000Z","msg":"條件：要奶共"},{"pid":"7796593b8763a8e9998b83e782f136d1ebe47693","tid":1890362,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"仆街政府，輸打贏要<br />\n<br />\n如果嗰個有心人係有一條或以上運作中嘅生產線，就已經orders (本地及海外)多到做唔切，仲使問政府攞研發基金?<br />\n<br />\n政府臨急抱佛腳，要本地口罩生產商，大量提供口罩，但又處處阻撓，係某啲政治取向嘅商家先有援助<br />\n<br />\n淋奠死全家啦"},{"pid":"e2f07641de9849700041f36e147892d23e5ade21","tid":1890362,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a97f66de3e9ab617f58c24ba5ab3df3d067a3e2","tid":1890362,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"期貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣好似炒燶石油咁,打後幾年要挨貴貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"佢肯出錢<br />\n即係預長期作戰<br />\n仲唔明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a61002cd85ed02b740fdc44b628a4c44a2ff680","tid":1890362,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}